    <title>Python学习笔记之1——字符串常用操作</title>
    <link href="http://aqsong.github.io/2017/03/29/python%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0%E4%B9%8B1%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6%E4%B8%B2%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C/"/>
    <id>http://aqsong.github.io/2017/03/29/python学习笔记之1——字符串常用操作/</id>
    <published>2017-03-29T13:33:13.000Z</published>
    <updated>2017-03-29T13:36:34.000Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><strong><em>本文持续更新，updated:2017-3-29。</em></strong></p>
<h3 id="len"><a href="#len" class="headerlink" title="len( )"></a>len( )</h3><p>&emsp;&emsp;获取字符串包含字符个数，包括空格在内。<br><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">strr = <span class="string">'abc '</span></div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> (len(strr))</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>&emsp;&emsp;输出结果为’4’。<br><a id="more"></a></p>
<h3 id="upper"><a href="#upper" class="headerlink" title="upper( )"></a>upper( )</h3><p>&emsp;&emsp;将字符串全部大写。<br><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">strr = <span class="string">'abc'</span></div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> (strr)</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>&emsp;&emsp;输出结果为’ABC’。</p>
<h3 id="lower"><a href="#lower" class="headerlink" title="lower( )"></a>lower( )</h3><p>&emsp;&emsp;将字符串全部小写。<br><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">strr = <span class="string">'ABC'</span></div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> (strr)</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>&emsp;&emsp;输出结果为’abc’。</p>
<h3 id="rstrip-lstrip-strip"><a href="#rstrip-lstrip-strip" class="headerlink" title="rstrip( ), lstrip( ), strip( )"></a>rstrip( ), lstrip( ), strip( )</h3><p>&emsp;&emsp;分别为删除字符串前端空白、后端空白以及两端空白。<br><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">strr = <span class="string">'  ab c  '</span></div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> (strr.rstrip())</div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> (strr.lstrip())</div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> (strr.strip())</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>&emsp;&emsp;输出结果分别为’ab c    ‘、’    ab c’、’ab c’。</p>
<h3 id="count"><a href="#count" class="headerlink" title="count( )"></a>count( )</h3><p>&emsp;&emsp;确定特定短语在字符串中出现次数。<br><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">strr = <span class="string">'What we eat is what we need.'</span></div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> (strr.lower().count())</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>&emsp;&emsp;输出结果为’2’。</p>
<h3 id="int-float"><a href="#int-float" class="headerlink" title="int( ), float( )"></a>int( ), float( )</h3><p>&emsp;&emsp;将字符串转换为整数、浮点数。</p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">strr = <span class="string">'4'</span></div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> (int(strr))</div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> (float(strr))</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>&emsp;&emsp;输出结果为’4’、’4.0’。</p>
]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;本文持续更新，updated:2017-3-29。&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;len&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#len&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;len( )&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;len( )&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;emsp;&amp;emsp;获取字符串包含字符个数，包括空格在内。&lt;br&gt;&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight python&quot;&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;gutter&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;1&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;2&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;code&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;strr = &lt;span class=&quot;string&quot;&gt;&#39;abc &#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;keyword&quot;&gt;print&lt;/span&gt; (len(strr))&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;emsp;&amp;emsp;输出结果为’4’。&lt;br&gt;
    
    </summary>
    
